Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:28.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Second L, and the one\Nwho I think is Kira, is Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.78,0:01:30.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Good evening.\NThis is Kiyomi Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.86,0:01:35.70,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frx348\fry12\frz26.747\fscx78.75\fscy126.25\move(568,443,524,442,20,4838)}Kiyomi Takada\NChosen as Kira's\NSpokesperson
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.19,0:01:33.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's words, which I\Nam about to tell you now,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.62,0:01:35.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,are to become the\Nlaw of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About our investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.53,0:01:39.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we should incorporate\NKiyomi Takada from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.26,0:01:42.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.63,0:01:44.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.83,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz347.455\pos(361,223)}Kira wants to have the room
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.83,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz347.455\pos(321,265)}checked for devices.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.83,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz347.455\pos(322,315)}I'm removing everything
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.08,0:01:45.83,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz347.455\pos(296,372)}before he sees them.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:45.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Remove the wiretaps-?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.23,0:01:47.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.80,0:01:48.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen Kiyomi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.04,0:01:51.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.48,0:01:55.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yagami is...Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.55,0:02:03.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All the pieces are set.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:05.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that things have\Ngone this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.39,0:02:07.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to head to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:10.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Rester.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.43,0:02:11.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.23,0:02:14.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you return to New York now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:15.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.13,0:02:17.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've decided to go to Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.40,0:02:21.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean that I'll be standing by\Nin New York while you're gone?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.77,0:02:22.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do I have to\Nreturn to New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.61,0:02:30.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never been on\Nan airplane by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to come back now,\Nand come with me to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.22,0:02:34.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.66,0:02:45.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As we expected,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.79,0:02:48.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yoshida Productions and\NNHN jumped at the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.60,0:02:51.65,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz9.561\move(419,55,402,55,0,3038)}Misa Amane!\NComeback at the NHN East West Pop
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Great Misa-Misa Comeback Plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's difficult to enter\NNHN right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:57.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but this will allow us to do it\Nwithout looking suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.71,0:03:01.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Mogi can go as her manager.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.68,0:03:04.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We definitely want someone\Nwho can freely enter NHN.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:07.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll also investigate through Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.62,0:03:11.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Near. Give me L.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.12,0:03:14.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is L... What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.39,0:03:20.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to arrest Kira and\NI'm here in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.10,0:03:22.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In Japan-?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.56,0:03:24.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he taking the time\Nto tell me that-?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:28.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L...You've contacted Takada
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.60,0:03:30.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and are investigating\NKira, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:34.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes... I'm investigating her myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.98,0:03:36.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.91,0:03:39.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, it's a given\Nthat we must investigate
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:44.05,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,NHN's Kiyomi Takada if\Nwe want to find Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.59,0:03:46.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So tell Takada that...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.62,0:03:52.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,SPK members have entered Japan\Nin order to arrest Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.66,0:03:54.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.23,0:03:57.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to lure Kira out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.40,0:04:00.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I also want you to add this:
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:06.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only four members\Nof the SPK, including myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.44,0:04:09.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira won't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.58,0:04:12.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll definitely try to kill us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:13.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.38,0:04:15.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,going to use that to beat him\Nat his own game.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:17.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat him at his own game, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.32,0:04:25.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine...Near...\NI'll accept your challenge!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.19,0:04:27.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.53,0:04:29.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.97,0:04:36.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then we may meet\Nface-to-face soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.60,0:04:37.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.84,0:04:41.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That will be something\Nto look forward to...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:45.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll bring this business with Kira\Nto an end once and for all...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.38,0:04:47.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it,\Nsince the beginning...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.55,0:04:55.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,this has been a one-on-one\Nbattle against L...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.96,0:05:01.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Only now, it's shifted to someone\Nwho's influenced by L.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:07.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine, Near.\NI'll come out if you're coming out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.47,0:05:10.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When we meet,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:14.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll see who's more prepared\Nand who can surpass the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.64,0:05:17.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens,\Nthe battle will end.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:21.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's when I'll begin\Nmy reign at the top!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.65,0:05:26.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,First, we have to figure out\Nour current situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.09,0:05:28.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L is Light Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.39,0:05:30.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.66,0:05:33.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's assume that there\Nis an L-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.70,0:05:36.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And there's another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.53,0:05:40.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Kira. He holds the notebook\Nand is using it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.10,0:05:46.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging by X-Kira's killings,\Nhe definitely has the Shinigami eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.31,0:05:52.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L-Kira and X-Kira plan to\Ncommunicate through Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.48,0:05:58.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I believe there are approximately\Ntwo ways to win against Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.39,0:06:01.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our first option...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.76,0:06:07.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is to kill L-Kira and X-Kira\Nand take the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:11.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But we will never resort to this method.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.60,0:06:12.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.70,0:06:14.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is not how we do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:16.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.41,0:06:18.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:21.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Killing people and getting\Nex post-facto justification
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:24.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,just by the fact that\Nthe killings have stopped...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.15,0:06:26.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the way that\NL and I do things.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.28,0:06:29.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L wouldn't be able to rest...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:33.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There would be no meaning to entrusting\Nthis case to his successors...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:51.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada, it's become well known that
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.51,0:06:53.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you receive an enormous amount\Nof fan mail every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:58.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I've heard it's about\Nan average of 200 letters a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:01.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,200 letters...\NI'm kind of jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.95,0:07:04.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- I don't even have time to read them.\N- With just audio and no video...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.79,0:07:06.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's quite boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.92,0:07:10.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should look through\Nthem even if they're fan letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.96,0:07:12.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.53,0:07:17.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep calm when you read\Nthe following note.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.30,0:07:19.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure not to let the people\Nlistening to this conversation
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,detect your surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.64,0:07:26.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The SPK has started to move.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.21,0:07:31.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,For your safety, you should\Nnot only accept messages...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.18,0:07:35.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but make demands to Kira as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.15,0:07:38.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light has moved on to the main topic.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.85,0:07:42.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't remain just\Na representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.06,0:07:46.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you reach out to Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.60,0:07:53.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a different job\Nthat T must to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.04,0:07:56.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In order to create\Nthe perfect world for Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.21,0:08:01.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to punish as Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.01,0:08:09.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. You'll do it well...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.49,0:08:14.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, you can give\Ninformation to Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that you don't want the SPK to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.36,0:08:23.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.23,0:08:27.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As I expected of Light. He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.81,0:08:33.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete... Delete...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.54,0:08:35.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.75,0:08:38.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyomi Takada...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.78,0:08:43.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.82,0:08:45.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's your message.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.95,0:08:50.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Send me a fan letter that I can\Ntell is from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.36,0:08:54.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Place within it...\NFive blank notebook pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.80,0:09:00.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue killing as usual\Nuntil I receive them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.64,0:09:02.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about after you receive them?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:07.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Continue killing using\Na fake notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:09.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.71,0:09:10.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Make a notebook that looks\Nas close to the original as possible...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.78,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and act as if you're killing\Nusing the fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.72,0:09:20.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:24.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God, what are you doing-?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.03,0:09:27.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's no need to question.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.16,0:09:29.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God is absolute...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:33.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My job is to do as God wishes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.39,0:09:56.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this show?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.56,0:09:58.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the program after Kira's Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.83,0:10:00.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're as unscrupulous as always.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.23,0:10:02.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Today, Miss Takada will introduce...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:08.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,her four female bodyguards who have\Npassed a rigorous screening process.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.77,0:10:13.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The 22nd Karate Title Champion,\NTatsumi Ooyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.64,0:10:17.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Former CIA agent Hal Lidner.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.68,0:10:21.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's an SPK member\Namong these people,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.55,0:10:23.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it would have to be Hal Lidner...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.58,0:10:26.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near is also trying to\Ninvestigate Takada...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.19,0:10:30.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A phantom killer has stabbed\Nsix people...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.99,0:10:34.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Who would I choose...\N- in Shinjuku's busy quarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.13,0:10:36.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- to be X-Kira?\N- There has been another slaying.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.80,0:10:41.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Children are to be taught about
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:45.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's existence and teachings\Nas mandatory education.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.34,0:10:48.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Takada was chosen because...\N- I think that there is nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.38,0:10:50.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- she is a Kira worshiper.\N- more important.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:56.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,X-Kira is someone who knows\Nthat Takada is a Kira-worshiper.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.28,0:11:00.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone who has a close,\Nintimate relationship with Takada...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.82,0:11:05.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira will not forgive any small crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.49,0:11:07.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,From now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:09.90,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,assume that any living person\Nis a target.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.91,0:11:26.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to hear Kira's voice...\Nhis thoughts once more.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:31.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that following Kira's teachings\Nexactly as ordered
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.82,0:11:34.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,is the quickest path to world peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:43.76,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(190,86)\fad(1001,959)}21st Century Discussion
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:43.76,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(391,23)\fad(1001,959)}Thinking about the
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.04,0:11:43.76,Death Note Signs/Titles Sm,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(391,86)\fad(1001,959)}Reconstruction of Japan
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:39.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it is of the utmost importance\Nthat young people do everything
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.43,0:11:43.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,in their power\Nto contribute to society from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.76,0:11:46.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If there are no orders or\Nwords from Kira,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.23,0:11:49.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,we need to believe that\Nit's all part of Kira's plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.44,0:11:54.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And make our own decisions\Nand take action.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.14,0:11:57.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- L-Kira is Light Yagami.\N- Kira's orders. Kira's Kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.68,0:11:59.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- It was Teru Mikami's own decision...\N-Spokesperson. Close since college.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- to contact Kiyomi Takada...\N-Coincidental past. Secret meetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.92,0:12:04.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,-in order to stop Demegawa's rampage.\N-Had notebook before our surveillance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:10.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything seems to fit...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.16,0:12:16.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why aren't I the headlining performer?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.83,0:12:20.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You said that I was the highlight of\Nthis year's East West Pop Song Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.57,0:12:22.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the highlight is the highlight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.64,0:12:25.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the headlining act is usually\Na leading figure...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:32.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should take precautions...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.58,0:12:37.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiyomi Takada...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.85,0:12:39.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She sure is stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.29,0:12:43.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She doesn't know that Light is just\Nusing her for his investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.76,0:12:46.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say that. You'll be killed if you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:49.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. That's why I whispered it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:52.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey-!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.63,0:12:54.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She snickered at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to kick her!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.40,0:12:58.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.54,0:13:04.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.78,0:13:07.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What was I doing?\NWhat about you, lady-?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.12,0:13:16.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidner, she's a good friend of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.49,0:13:19.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't be rough with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:22.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Miss Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.60,0:13:23.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.33,0:13:27.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Misa-Misa!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.77,0:13:28.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.10,0:13:33.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was so frustrating-!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.74,0:13:37.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L. If Mr. Aizawa is there...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.81,0:13:40.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,May I talk to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.88,0:13:44.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, this is Aizawa.\NWhat is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:51.18,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you videotape and wiretap L\Nand Takada's meetings?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:54.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. We only have wiretaps now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.53,0:14:00.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. Only wiretaps now.\NThank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.40,0:14:03.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's only wiretaps...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.34,0:14:05.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then we can assume that L-Kira\Nand X-Kira
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.77,0:14:08.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,are contacting each other\Nthrough Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.81,0:14:11.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case,\Nthen Lidner is in increasing danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.78,0:14:18.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's important is for L to turn\Nhis attention to Lidner and Takada.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.62,0:14:21.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll investigate Mikami\Nwhile his attention is on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.52,0:14:24.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How are things, Gevanni?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:29.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About Mikami...\NIt's strangely easy to follow him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.90,0:14:31.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't try to hide and
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.53,0:14:35.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,has been living normally in\Nthe same place for the past four years.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.04,0:14:38.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's prosecuting people\Nenthusiastically at his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:41.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think that he can be X-Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:45.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. There is a high possibility\Nthat Mikami is X-Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please be careful...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.25,0:14:50.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't enter his room yet,\Njust keep watch over him...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.85,0:14:51.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.55,0:14:58.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez. How many meetings\Ndo I have to have with NHN?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:15:03.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And how many times have only I been told,\N"Be careful about what you say"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.56,0:15:04.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.73,0:15:06.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. I'll ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.87,0:15:13.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Misa-Misa. Takada is asking if\Nyou would like to have dinner together.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.64,0:15:14.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:17.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That Kiyomi... What does she want?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.38,0:15:20.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.75,0:15:22.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Pop Song Festival emcee\Nand the main headliner
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:25.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,should have dinner together\Nat least once...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.89,0:15:26.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell her, "Okay."
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.42,0:15:30.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.93,0:15:33.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Takada, she agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.96,0:15:35.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Lidner, book a nice private room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.30,0:15:41.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.17,0:15:43.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would like you to attend as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.37,0:15:44.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.59,0:16:10.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Amane, I'm sorry\Nthis is so late at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.23,0:16:13.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It just had to be after News 9 finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.30,0:16:17.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem. I don't mind.\NI'm a night owl anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.65,0:16:29.08,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard for me to say if\Nyou ask, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:36.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your boyfriend seems busy.\NDo you still see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.86,0:16:42.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why that... She knows that\Nshe can see him, but I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.70,0:16:43.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Such a...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.77,0:16:49.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I do. He's a lot more affectionate\Nthan he looks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.40,0:16:52.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He clings onto me so much as soon as\Nhe comes home every night!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.71,0:16:57.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... You're doing well.\NThank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:00.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, since you're the emcee,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.68,0:17:03.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to tell you this\Nin advance, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.88,0:17:07.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to announce my engagement\Nto him at the Pop Music Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Does he...know about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.19,0:17:17.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. It's an engagement.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.30,0:17:18.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't do it by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.50,0:17:22.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He promised me more\Nthan a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.57,0:17:24.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think it would make\Nthings more exciting if
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.74,0:17:26.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I announced it at\Nthe Pop Music Festival, Miss Emcee?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.85,0:17:36.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.58,0:17:38.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be great if you could.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.19,0:17:40.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, "if I could"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.02,0:17:44.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to let me do it?\NOr are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.03,0:17:47.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Going to have me killed by Kira-?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.33,0:17:54.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not.\NOnly Kira decides who to punish.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.07,0:17:59.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not involved.\NI think of you as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.14,0:18:01.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say such depressing things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any intention\Nof killing anyone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.05,0:18:07.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,no matter how horrible they may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:13.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever.\NI used to like Kira as well, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.52,0:18:16.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light's going to catch Kira soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:24.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When he's caught,\Nnothing good will happen to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll probably get...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.43,0:18:28.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,executed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.77,0:18:32.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Miss Takada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:33.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:45.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Kiyomi... I'm Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.69,0:18:48.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,With me...You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.19,0:18:51.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,going to become the goddess\Nof the new world...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:57.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Amane.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.53,0:18:59.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.13,0:19:01.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was unpleasant.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.57,0:19:04.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...the same to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.71,0:19:07.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I should have waited\Nto invite you to dinner
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.11,0:19:09.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,until after you had become\Nmore mature
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.14,0:19:12.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and learned some manners.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.25,0:19:14.34,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.41,0:19:17.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm older than you are, Little Kiyomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.68,0:19:19.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, doesn't leaving the table\Nfor something like this
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.05,0:19:21.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,make you the more childish one?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mochi...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.51,0:19:43.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for waiting...\NHow are you-?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A-Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.01,0:19:49.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. I won.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.05,0:19:50.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Won?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.92,0:19:52.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. It was a cinch-!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About tonight's conversation between\NTakada and Amane...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.96,0:19:59.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I could only assume that\Nthey were fighting over...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.99,0:20:03.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,which one was\NLight Yagami's girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.67,0:20:05.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.70,0:20:07.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All that I can say from this is...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light Yagami is popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.14,0:20:14.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Takada and Amane adore\NLight Yagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.84,0:20:16.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, be serious about this...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.58,0:20:19.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a problem if\Nthey seriously like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.68,0:20:21.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They won't easily betray him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.08,0:20:24.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, he can make them do\Nwhatever he wants them to do...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.53,0:20:37.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.20,0:20:39.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with that, lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.23,0:20:42.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wearing such\Na short skirt even though it's winter...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.64,0:20:44.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You were tempting me, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.14,0:20:45.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.74,0:20:52.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A cell phone-?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.28,0:20:56.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami has taken out a notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.42,0:21:02.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Delete...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.96,0:21:05.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He's writing in it.\NCould that be it...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:07.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mikami's getting off.
